inputs.name: Which Face
inputs.description: Face select including Face 0, Face 1, Face 2, Face 3, Face 4, Any; Track any face if choosing Any

inputs.name: Facial Expression
inputs.description: Expression to detect including Happy, Angry, Surprise, Disgust, Fear, Sad, Neutral

outputs.name: Begin
outputs.description: Execute the next node when the expression begins

outputs.name: Stay
outputs.description: Keep executing the next node when the expression stays

outputs.name: End
outputs.description: Execute the next node when the expression ends

outputs.name: None
outputs.description: Keep executing the next node when the expression is not detected
